snippet.title: ValiDate: Struggling Singles in your Area coming September 2022!
snippet.description:
Play as Malik, Inaya, Emhari and Isabelle in ValiDate: Struggling Singles in your Area. Coming September 2022 to PC/Mac, Nintendo Switch and Xbox One and Series X|S!

Wishlist us on Steam here: http://steam.validategame.com/

Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/ValiDateGame
